node.text:
This Youth Mental Health Day, @shannonsinghhh is using her platform to spread positivity and has launched her social media campaign #ilovemine. 

At 23 years old, @shannonsinghhh wants to encourage everyone to start being kinder to themselves and to make social media a more
positive place. She says “Rather than giving our ‘likes’ to other people, we should be liking ourselves and celebrating who we are.”

@shannonsinghhh shares her top tips on finding self-confidence, the importance of a strong support network and what she does daily to keep her mental health in check.

node.title: Youth Mental Health Day with Shannon Singh
